#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
	int t,n,sum,i,j;
	cin>>t;
	while(t--)
	{
		cin>>n;
		for(i=1;i<=n;i++)
		{
			j=i;
			sum=0;
			while(j!=0)
			{
				sum+=j%10;
				j=j/10;
			}
			if(sum+i==n)
			{
				break;
			}
		}
		if(i==n+1)
		cout<<"NONE\n";
		else
		cout<<i<<endl;
	}
	return 0;
}
